```scheme
(define A (matrix/make (list (list 6 -1 0)
                              (list -1 5 -1)
                              (list 0 -1 4))))

(define evals (linalg/eigenvalues A))

(list 'A A 'eigenvalues evals)
```
[VISUAL: text output showing three eigenvalues]
<!-- BUILD: run; print result -->

**Specialized 3×3 eigenvalue solver** (direct method).

```scheme
(define A (matrix/make (list (list 1 0 0)
                              (list 0 2 0)
                              (list 0 0 3))))

(define evals (linalg/eigenvalues-3x3 A))

(list 'A A 'eigenvalues-3x3 evals)
```
[VISUAL: text output showing [1, 2, 3]]
<!-- BUILD: run; verify linalg/eigenvalues-3x3; print result -->

**Eigenvectors** — the directions associated with each eigenvalue.

```scheme
