                              (list 2 3))))

(define evecs (linalg/eigenvectors A))

(list 'A A 'eigenvectors evecs)
```
[VISUAL: text output showing a list of eigenvectors (could be a list of vectors or a tagged structure)]
<!-- BUILD: run; verify linalg/eigenvectors; print result -->

**Eigenvalues and eigenvectors of a symmetric 3×3 matrix.**

```scheme
(define S (matrix/make (list (list 4 1 1)
                              (list 1 4 1)
                              (list 1 1 4))))

(define evals (linalg/eigenvalues S))
(define evecs (linalg/eigenvectors S))

(list 'S S 'eigenvalues evals 'eigenvectors evecs)
```
[VISUAL: text output showing eigenvalues and corresponding eigenvectors]
<!-- BUILD: run; print result -->

**Characteristic polynomial** — det(A - λI), whose roots are the eigenvalues.

```scheme
(define A (matrix/make (list (list 5 2)
                              (list 2 1))))

(define char-poly (linalg/characteristic-poly A))

(list 'A A 'characteristic-polynomial char-poly)
```
[VISUAL: text output showing a polynomial (symbolic or coefficient list)]
