(define u (vec/make 1 1))

(define proj (linalg/project v u))

(list 'v v 'u u 'projection proj)
```
[VISUAL: text output showing the projection]
<!-- BUILD: run; print result -->

**Projection onto the column space of a matrix** (conceptually related to least-squares).

```scheme
(define A (matrix/make (list (list 1 0)
                              (list 0 1)
                              (list 1 1))))
(define b (matrix/make (list (list 1) (list 1) (list 2))))

(define proj (matrix/* A (linalg/least-squares A b)))

(list 'b b 'projection-onto-col-space proj)
```
