                                     (list 0 0))))

(define v (matrix/make (list (list 3) (list 4))))
(define Pv (matrix/* ProjectX v))

(list 'ProjectX ProjectX 'v v 'Pv Pv)
```
[VISUAL: text output showing (3,4) → (3,0)]
<!-- BUILD: run; print result -->

**Transform a square** — apply a matrix to each vertex.

